Gosh, it's Young Jin.

775
00:25:08,038 --> 00:25:10,408
(1 snow crab is out.)

776
00:25:10,678 --> 00:25:12,777
We're losing 120 dollars each time.

777
00:25:12,778 --> 00:25:14,578
It looks about 900g.

778
00:25:15,118 --> 00:25:16,548
I'm so hungry.

779
00:25:16,888 --> 00:25:18,548
- Let's do it.
- We have to.

780
00:25:18,718 --> 00:25:20,394
We need to draw a chance card. Otherwise, it won't work.

781
00:25:20,418 --> 00:25:21,658
Jong Min, draw one.

782
00:25:22,118 --> 00:25:23,527
Pick either the green or the yellow card.

783
00:25:23,528 --> 00:25:24,557
(Drawing their fourth chance card)

784
00:25:24,558 --> 00:25:25,588
Green or yellow.

785
00:25:25,858 --> 00:25:27,228
Please.

786
00:25:27,798 --> 00:25:29,297
(What kind of chance will they get?)

787
00:25:29,298 --> 00:25:30,597
Let it be "replay the entire song."

788
00:25:30,598 --> 00:25:31,697
Please.

789
00:25:31,698 --> 00:25:32,767
- Please.
- If you picked "exchange spots,"

790
00:25:32,768 --> 00:25:33,838
you'd better go home.

791
00:25:34,268 --> 00:25:35,468
(What kind of chance is it?)

792
00:25:35,568 --> 00:25:37,007
"Replay the entire song for one person."

793
00:25:37,008 --> 00:25:38,408
- We're doomed.
- One person alone?

794
00:25:38,668 --> 00:25:39,778
All right, everyone.

795
00:25:40,208 --> 00:25:42,878
For the next mission, we'll replay the entire song...

796
00:25:43,378 --> 00:25:45,307
- for one member only.
- Oh, no.

797
00:25:45,308 --> 00:25:47,277
- Lim Cheol, you have to do it.
- No.

798
00:25:47,278 --> 00:25:48,917
- Give it a try.
- No.

799
00:25:48,918 --> 00:25:50,618
I'm also one of the members.

800
00:25:50,918 --> 00:25:53,287
- I'm a fool like all of you.
- No.

801
00:25:53,288 --> 00:25:55,087
- I may look smart among you, - No, you're a genius.

802
00:25:55,088 --> 00:25:56,608
- but I'm actually a fool.
- You brat.

803
00:25:56,888 --> 00:25:58,857
- Listen to me carefully.
- I'm really dumb.

804
00:25:58,858 --> 00:25:59,927
- No, you aren't dumb.
- You weakling.

805
00:25:59,928 --> 00:26:00,928
You weakling.

806
00:26:00,929 --> 00:26:02,468
- Hey, you think you're dumb?
- Hey.

807
00:26:02,598 --> 00:26:03,967
We're dumb airheads.

808
00:26:03,968 --> 00:26:05,367
We're extremely foolish.

809
00:26:05,368 --> 00:26:06,928
Since you're just dumb, you must do it.

810
00:26:07,368 --> 00:26:09,128
I don't even know the multiplication tables.

811
00:26:09,168 --> 00:26:10,528
- Hurry up and do it.
- Seriously?

812
00:26:10,608 --> 00:26:11,737
- In that case...
- You're the only one who can do it.

813
00:26:11,738 --> 00:26:12,838
In that case,

814
00:26:13,408 --> 00:26:15,377
I just need to listen to this part and the last one.

815
00:26:15,378 --> 00:26:17,247
- Right.
- All the lyrics for those parts.

816
00:26:17,248 --> 00:26:18,978
You can do it.

817
00:26:19,148 --> 00:26:20,348
DinDin, we're almost there.

818
00:26:20,478 --> 00:26:23,088
- You can do it.
- Wait. DinDin, please listen.

819
00:26:23,348 --> 00:26:24,748
- Let's go.
- Everyone.

820
00:26:25,418 --> 00:26:27,058
