830
00:26:43,409 --> 00:26:45,289
- I'll go instead.
- Sit back down immediately.

831
00:26:45,808 --> 00:26:48,278
Sit back down. What are you doing?

832
00:26:48,478 --> 00:26:49,907
- I'll go.
- Do you want to ruin the team?

833
00:26:49,908 --> 00:26:50,948
Sit back down right away.

834
00:26:51,308 --> 00:26:52,868
This game isn't for you. Sit back down.

835
00:26:53,178 --> 00:26:54,178
It's so unfair.

836
00:26:54,578 --> 00:26:55,788
Everyone, stay still.

837
00:26:55,918 --> 00:26:57,088
You fool, go outside.

838
00:26:58,088 --> 00:26:59,157
- You fool, go outside.
- DinDin.

839
00:26:59,158 --> 00:27:00,817
You're really a genius.

840
00:27:00,818 --> 00:27:03,218
- Do you want me to go instead?
- I told you to stay seated.

841
00:27:03,788 --> 00:27:05,487
This is where the respect ends.

842
00:27:05,488 --> 00:27:06,528
Sit back down.

843
00:27:07,058 --> 00:27:08,658
Please sit down for the team.

844
00:27:08,958 --> 00:27:10,427
- Gosh, I don't feel confident.
- You can do it.

845
00:27:10,428 --> 00:27:11,628
You can do it.

846
00:27:12,268 --> 00:27:13,268
(Shouting)

847
00:27:13,768 --> 00:27:14,768
(Shouting)

848
00:27:15,338 --> 00:27:16,408
Where is it?

849
00:27:16,538 --> 00:27:17,538
(Shouting)

850
00:27:17,938 --> 00:27:20,278
- Hurry up and play.
- Here we go.

851
00:27:20,738 --> 00:27:23,278
(Measures for DinDin and Se Yoon)

852
00:27:23,908 --> 00:27:26,148
(They don't know the lyrics from here on.)

853
00:27:26,618 --> 00:27:30,048
(Measure for Joon)

854
00:27:33,618 --> 00:27:39,698
(Everyone together)

855
00:27:40,558 --> 00:27:42,598
(The fourth chance ended.)

856
00:27:43,268 --> 00:27:44,468
- They regret...
- Gosh.

857
00:27:44,798 --> 00:27:46,237
- You're back.
- Be quiet.

858
00:27:46,238 --> 00:27:48,837
- Tell us.
- Be quiet.

859
00:27:48,838 --> 00:27:50,008
He's back.

860
00:27:50,168 --> 00:27:52,608
Don't talk to him.

861
00:27:53,138 --> 00:27:54,808
Be quiet. Do whatever DinDin says.

862
00:27:55,508 --> 00:27:58,607
"They regret a lot not following through."

863
00:27:58,608 --> 00:27:59,618
That's correct.

864
00:27:59,678 --> 00:28:01,217
