"There are excuses for failing..."

870
00:28:11,428 --> 00:28:13,328
"and reasons to blame for losing."

871
00:28:13,528 --> 00:28:15,008
- "For losing?" - That's how it ends.

872
00:28:15,868 --> 00:28:16,927
