873
00:28:16,928 --> 00:28:17,967
"after doing something wrong?"

874
00:28:17,968 --> 00:28:19,268
No, it's "and reasons."

875
00:28:19,368 --> 00:28:20,967
"And reasons to blame for losing."

876
00:28:20,968 --> 00:28:23,168
"And reasons to blame for losing."

877
00:28:23,408 --> 00:28:24,537
