884
00:28:36,788 --> 00:28:39,188
I remember it now. Darn it.

885
00:28:39,988 --> 00:28:42,158
There was the word "poop."

886
00:28:42,288 --> 00:28:43,987
- "Poop?" - I heard something like "byeon."

887
00:28:43,988 --> 00:28:44,988
The word must be "excuses."

888
00:28:44,989 --> 00:28:48,758
(Make excuses)

889
00:28:49,298 --> 00:28:50,697
- It's "excuses." - Gosh.

890
00:28:50,698 --> 00:28:51,827
- Byeon.
- "Make excuses..."

891
00:28:51,828 --> 00:28:53,067
- "for not doing well." - Right.

892
00:28:53,068 --> 00:28:54,568
"Make excuses for not doing well."

893
00:28:54,938 --> 00:28:56,637
Is it "not trying" or "not doing well?"

894
00:28:56,638 --> 00:28:57,638
(Make excuses for not doing well)

895
00:28:57,639 --> 00:28:58,708
"Not doing well?"

896
00:28:59,338 --> 00:29:00,537
"Not doing well."

897
00:29:00,538 --> 00:29:01,637
I think you're right.

898
00:29:01,638 --> 00:29:02,807
Go with "not doing well."

899
00:29:02,808 --> 00:29:04,107
- "Not doing well." - "Not doing well?"

900
00:29:04,108 --> 00:29:05,708
- Make excuses for not doing well - Yes.

901
00:29:05,808 --> 00:29:06,918
Make excuses.

902
00:29:07,548 --> 00:29:08,748
- "Make excuses?" - Yes.

903
00:29:09,518 --> 00:29:11,348
I think it ends with "make excuses."

904
00:29:12,018 --> 00:29:13,688
But they don't rhyme.

905
00:29:13,958 --> 00:29:15,487
There was nothing after that.

906
00:29:15,488 --> 00:29:16,857
No, wait.

907
00:29:16,858 --> 00:29:18,557
The end of the song was unusually abrupt.

908
00:29:18,558 --> 00:29:19,627
Exactly.

909
00:29:19,628 --> 00:29:24,867
(Lyrics)

910
00:29:24,868 --> 00:29:26,437
(Ending abruptly)

911
00:29:26,438 --> 00:29:27,837
- "Make excuses?" - "For not doing well..."

912
00:29:27,838 --> 00:29:29,507
Yes.

913
00:29:29,508 --> 00:29:31,767
- The ending was strange.
- Each measure has eight characters.

914
00:29:31,768 --> 00:29:32,837
It must be "make excuses..."

915
00:29:32,838 --> 00:29:34,307
- "for not doing well." - That's how it ends.

916
00:29:34,308 --> 00:29:35,308
- "Make excuses." - Wait.

917
00:29:35,308 --> 00:29:36,308
If it's "not following through,"

918
00:29:36,309 --> 00:29:37,869
shouldn't the second part end the same?

919
00:29:38,078 --> 00:29:39,777
"They regret not following through."

920
00:29:39,778 --> 00:29:40,778
- "Not trying." - "Not trying."

921
00:29:40,779 --> 00:29:41,948
"Not doing well."

922
00:29:42,348 --> 00:29:44,418
- Is there "well?" - Without doing well...

923
00:29:45,118 --> 00:29:46,887
"They regret not following through..."

924
00:29:46,888 --> 00:29:48,217
"and make excuses for not even trying."

925
00:29:48,218 --> 00:29:49,227
That's right.

926
00:29:49,228 --> 00:29:50,527
"They regret not following through..."

927
00:29:50,528 --> 00:29:52,027
"and make excuses for not even trying."

928
00:29:52,028 --> 00:29:53,697
- This is correct.
- "Excuses for not even trying."

929
00:29:53,698 --> 00:29:55,397
Okay. "They regret not following through."

930
00:29:55,398 --> 00:29:57,628
I'll tell you the last part.

931
00:29:57,798 --> 00:29:59,697
"Our home is full of fun and happiness."

932
00:29:59,698 --> 00:30:00,767
"And happiness."

933
00:30:00,768 --> 00:30:02,167
- "You should come over." - "You should come over,"

934
00:30:02,168 --> 00:30:03,408
- "ha, ha, ha." - That's right.

935
00:30:04,068 --> 00:30:05,237
- I think that's right.
- That's right.

936
00:30:05,238 --> 00:30:06,507
Let's try from the start.

937
00:30:06,508 --> 00:30:09,178
We just need to go over them.

938
00:30:09,308 --> 00:30:10,947
There are excuses for failing

939
00:30:10,948 --> 00:30:12,447
as well as reasons...

940
00:30:12,448 --> 00:30:14,328
- It's "and." - And reasons to blame for losing

941
00:30:14,448 --> 00:30:16,148
There are excuses for failing

942
00:30:16,788 --> 00:30:18,547
Reasons to blame for losing

943
00:30:18,548 --> 00:30:20,658
- "And reasons." - And reasons to blame for losing

944
00:30:21,358 --> 00:30:23,228
(This isn't reassuring.)

945
00:30:23,388 --> 00:30:24,987
- What's after "our home?" - I can't do this.

946
00:30:24,988 --> 00:30:26,558
Hang in there, you fool.

947
00:30:26,698 --> 00:30:28,857
We only have one snow crab left.

948
00:30:28,858 --> 00:30:30,227
Tell me again. What comes after "our home?"

949
00:30:30,228 --> 00:30:31,997
If we fail this time, we won't get any snow crabs.

950
00:30:31,998 --> 00:30:33,138
Okay, let's go.

951
00:30:33,638 --> 00:30:34,767
We have to focus.

952
