Everyone, this is your fifth try.

953
00:30:37,538 --> 00:30:40,178
All right, play the song.

954
00:30:40,408 --> 00:30:41,608
It's our last chance. Please.

955
00:30:43,278 --> 00:30:45,778
("Men of the Bath House," Keep Your Snow Crab)

956
00:30:46,018 --> 00:30:49,587
(Because the world we live in is trivial after all)

957
00:30:49,588 --> 00:30:52,957
(He tells us to cherish and love one another)

958
00:30:52,958 --> 00:30:54,657
(It's no one's fault)

959
00:30:54,658 --> 00:30:56,757
(That some live well)

960
00:30:56,758 --> 00:31:00,058
(While others don't)

961
00:31:00,358 --> 00:31:02,427
(There are excuses for failing)

962
00:31:02,428 --> 00:31:04,297
(Reasons to blame for losing)

963
00:31:04,298 --> 00:31:05,827
- They regret not following through - Wrong.

964
00:31:05,828 --> 00:31:07,337
I told you many times that it's "and reasons."

965
00:31:07,338 --> 00:31:08,468
It's "and reasons."

966
00:31:09,268 --> 00:31:11,408
(Their fifth try fails.)

967
00:31:11,568 --> 00:31:13,678
