972
00:31:21,918 --> 00:31:23,218
It's "and reasons."

973
00:31:23,348 --> 00:31:24,748
- Did I forget to say "and?" - Yes.

974
00:31:24,848 --> 00:31:25,988
Is that why I got it wrong?

975
00:31:26,488 --> 00:31:27,718
That's wrong.

976
00:31:27,888 --> 00:31:28,888
Yes.

977
00:31:28,958 --> 00:31:30,438
Jong Min, pull out two of your teeth.

978
00:31:31,328 --> 00:31:32,487
Now...

979
00:31:32,488 --> 00:31:34,328
- So that you come to your senses.
- Everyone.

980
00:31:35,298 --> 00:31:37,227
We'll take out the snow crab.

981
00:31:37,228 --> 00:31:38,898
We could've succeeded this time.

982
00:31:39,268 --> 00:31:40,748
We could've checked the right answer.

983
00:31:40,898 --> 00:31:43,308
- But...
- We're doomed.

984
