(2 hours ago when his face wasn't hot)

988
00:31:52,678 --> 00:31:53,817
This is crazy.

989
00:31:53,818 --> 00:31:55,917
All right, we just need to stay alert.

990
00:31:55,918 --> 00:31:56,918
There's no need to sing the melody.

991
00:31:56,919 --> 00:31:58,394
- Jong Min.
- Just focus on the lyrics.

992
00:31:58,418 --> 00:31:59,457
Can you do it well?

993
00:31:59,458 --> 00:32:00,617
- Okay.
- Okay.

994
00:32:00,618 --> 00:32:01,657
You can do it.

995
00:32:01,658 --> 00:32:03,387
- We can do it.
- "And reasons to blame for losing."

996
00:32:03,388 --> 00:32:04,487
(Saying "and reasons" is challenging.)

997
00:32:04,488 --> 00:32:05,488
All right.

998
00:32:05,489 --> 00:32:06,597
- Everyone.
- "Blame for losing."

999
00:32:06,598 --> 00:32:08,934
- This is your sixth attempt.
- Remember to lift your hand.

1000
00:32:08,958 --> 00:32:09,967
Okay.

1001
00:32:09,968 --> 00:32:11,898
Play the song.

1002
00:32:13,398 --> 00:32:14,997
("Men of the Bath House")

1003
00:32:14,998 --> 00:32:16,708
(Keep Your Monkfish Suyuk)

1004
00:32:17,638 --> 00:32:21,037
(Because the world we live in is trivial after all)

1005
