1011
00:32:38,228 --> 00:32:39,257
Next.

1012
00:32:39,258 --> 00:32:41,127
(There are excuses for failing)

1013
00:32:41,128 --> 00:32:43,227
(Also reasons to blame for losing)

1014
00:32:43,228 --> 00:32:44,597
Wrong.

1015
00:32:44,598 --> 00:32:45,628
What?

1016
00:32:46,338 --> 00:32:50,207
(Jong Min failed.)

1017
00:32:50,208 --> 00:32:51,268
What?

1018
00:32:51,608 --> 00:32:54,038
(Their sixth try fails.)

1019
00:32:54,878 --> 00:32:58,648
(They aren't so disappointed because they didn't expect much.)

1020
00:33:01,618 --> 00:33:05,648
(He still needs to get his act together.)

1021
00:33:07,058 --> 00:33:09,018
Jong Min, are you awake now?

1022
00:33:09,158 --> 00:33:10,257
Are you awake now?

1023
00:33:10,258 --> 00:33:12,227
Stop scolding me. You're making me nervous.

1024
00:33:12,228 --> 00:33:14,597
- You know what I noticed?
- You didn't get it right.

1025
00:33:14,598 --> 00:33:16,374
