1029
00:33:21,298 --> 00:33:22,698
Jong Min, what's wrong with you?

1030
00:33:22,908 --> 00:33:24,807
Jong Min, we didn't say anything to you.

1031
00:33:24,808 --> 00:33:26,338
Why are you so nervous?

1032
00:33:27,108 --> 00:33:29,237
Please take out the dish.

1033
00:33:29,238 --> 00:33:30,507
(Monkfish suyuk is out.)

1034
00:33:30,508 --> 00:33:31,777
We've never been...

1035
