2062
01:11:57,114 --> 01:11:59,084
(Out of 5, 2 will go to a popular restaurant.)

2063
01:11:59,654 --> 01:12:01,954
(Three will go to a popular spot with an amazing view.)

2064
01:12:02,254 --> 01:12:04,784
(Depending on which car they choose, )

2065
01:12:05,154 --> 01:12:08,224
(their fates will change.)

2066
01:12:08,524 --> 01:12:12,194
(Where will the members head to?)

2067
01:12:12,794 --> 01:12:15,833
The order is Se Yoon, DinDin, Jong Min, Seon Ho, and Joon.

2068
01:12:15,834 --> 01:12:17,480
(Order of arrival: Se Yoon, DinDin, Jong Min, Seon Ho, Joon)

2069
01:12:17,504 --> 01:12:18,703
All right. Choose one.

2070
01:12:18,704 --> 01:12:19,773
